  "texts": [
    "This method drastically reduces the complexity to O(M N 2), significantly speeding up the identification of nondominated fronts and minimizing the computational resources required.",
    "This enhancement highlights the critical importance of algorithmic efficiency in the context of complex optimization challenges, further establishing NSGA-II as a key framework in the development of efficient evolutionary algorithms.NSGA-II's methodical approach to multiobjective optimization combines simplicity with effectiveness.",
    "It begins with the formation of a combined population that includes both parent and children populations, thereby ensuring a blend of historical and current genetic information.",
    "This process not only facilitates elitism by preserving high-quality solutions but also prioritizes the selection of the best solutions from the foremost nondominated set.",
    "The algorithm employs a crowded-distance metric to ensure diversity and quality in the selection process, balancing exploration and exploitation within the search space."
